dataset.title: A new early diverging thalattosuchian (Crocodylomorpha) from the Early Jurassic (Pliensbachian) of Dorset, U. K. and implications for the origin and evolution of the group

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Wilberg, Eric W., Godoy, Pedro L., Griffiths, Elizabeth F., Turner, Alan H., Benson, Roger B. J. (2023): A new early diverging thalattosuchian (Crocodylomorpha) from the Early Jurassic (Pliensbachian) of Dorset, U. K. and implications for the origin and evolution of the group. Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology CLXVI (CLXVI): 1-23, DOI: 10.1080/02724634.2022.2161909, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.1080/02724634.2022.2161909
